page.title: 03LANDSCAPE
page.content: Taking a line from the junction of Park Lane and Padholm Rd eastward to the edge of the area the landscape shows 3 main changes. 1)One third of the area consists of the Eastfields council housing estate. 2)From Carr Dyke the Fengate area is designated an industrial area.It is dominated by Frank Perkins Engine factory.Therest of the area consists of open plan warehouses, small factories,wholesalers and service companies which often serve the motor industries. 3)The eastern third is a rural area which is typical of the Fens.Here the land is flat and hedge_less.A few farm buildings can be seen.
